{"data": [{"id": "4743729", "title": "Kforce: Betting On A Robust Labor Market Recovery", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesswomen meeting in modern conference room\" data-id=\"2155192264\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MoMo Productions</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong> </strong></h2> <h2><strong>Investment Thesis</strong></h2> <p>I believe that Kforce (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KFRC\" title=\"Kforce Inc.\">KFRC</a></span>) is a strong buy, and I expect its share price to exceed $85 in the coming 12 months (~40% return). The stock price has fallen from its 2021 highs (above $80) to the current $60 level due to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743729-kforce-betting-on-a-robust-labor-market-recovery", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 05:19:09"}, {"id": "4743728", "title": "EQWL: A Low-Valuation Equal-Weight ETF, Outperforming Peers But Lagging The S&P 500 Index", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"New York Stock Exchange Building\" data-id=\"1042838398\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1153px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Ivan Chertok</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Funds using an equal-weight approach come out as an interesting option to diversify risk and mitigate excess volatility, as this allocation structure helps avoid stock concentration in an environment where the stock market gains have significantly increased the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743728-eqwl-low-valuation-equal-weight-etf-outperforming-peers-but-lagging-sp500-index", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 05:06:46"}, {"id": "4743726", "title": "Consumer Price Index: Inflation Edges Up To 2.75% In November", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CPI, consumer price index concept. Wooden block with CPI word and stack of coins and increasing graph with shopping cart icon. Goods price inflation and inflation rising. Impact on economic growth\" data-id=\"2078053280\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Ratana21</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Jennifer Nash</em></p> <p>Inflation rose slightly in November. According to the Bureau of Labor Statistics, the headline figure for the Consumer Price Index rose to 2.75% year-over-year, right in line with economist expectations.</p> <p>Additionally, core CPI came in at</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743726-consumer-price-index-inflation-edges-up-to-2-75-percent-in-november", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 03:30:00"}, {"id": "4743721", "title": "Phathom Pharmaceuticals: The Large Drop Is, Well, Unfathomable", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Failure Concept\" data-id=\"1726514483\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4660604-phathom-pharma-is-a-buy-before-july-pdufa\">covered</a> <b>Phathom Pharmaceuticals, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PHAT\" title=\"Phathom Pharmaceuticals, Inc.\">PHAT</a></span>) in January. PHAT had a major label expansion in July. They got their approval successfully. Nothing much happened to the stock. Then between August and September, the stock suddenly doubled. This was right after the </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743721-phathom-pharmaceuticals-the-large-drop-is-well-unfathomable", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 02:41:21"}, {"id": "4743720", "title": "ETY: Decent Performance, But Portfolio Remains Very Concentrated", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621167/image_88621167.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bull and bear figurines on top of stack of quarters\" data-id=\"88621167\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1153px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621167/image_88621167.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, htt