_2136674540.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Boeing 777X test flight in February of 2020 in the skies over Spokane, Washington USA.\" data-id=\"2136674540\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136674540/image_2136674540.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136674540/image_2136674540.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136674540/image_2136674540.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136674540/image_2136674540.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136674540/image_2136674540.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136674540/image_2136674540.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136674540/image_2136674540.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136674540/image_2136674540.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jon Tetzlaff</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>On the day The Boeing Company (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BA\" title=\"The Boeing Company\">BA</a></span>) <a href=\"https://apnews.com/article/boeing-production-max-airplane-faa-seattle-ea1da9b7af67c1406eee7fdd61313bb1\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://apnews.com/article/boeing-production-max-airplane-faa-seattle-ea1da9b7af67c1406eee7fdd61313bb1\" target=\"_blank\">restarted production</a> on the Boeing 737 MAX program, the US jet maker also posted its order and delivery figures for the month of November. The two news items marked the reality of deliveries</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136674540/image_2136674540.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743718-boeing-hits-a-new-low-on-airplane-deliveries", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 02:31:50"}, {"id": "4743717", "title": "AMD: 2 Reasons To Be Greedy When Others Are Fearful", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157591493/image_157591493.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Afraid to loose money\" data-id=\"157591493\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157591493/image_157591493.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157591493/image_157591493.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157591493/image_157591493.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157591493/image_157591493.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157591493/image_157591493.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157591493/image_157591493.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157591493/image_157591493.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157591493/image_157591493.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MediaProduction</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>AMD stock: previous thesis and Q3 earnings</h2> <p>I last wrote on <b>Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.</b> (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMD#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.\">AMD</a>) back in October 2024. As reflected in the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4730137-amd-q3-preview-status-of-the-cycle\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723549-amd-zt-systems-acquisition-improves-ai-positioning-rating-upgrade\">article\u2019s title</a>, \u201cAMD Q3 Preview: Status Of The Cycle\u201d, it was a preview</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157591493/image_157591493.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743717-amd-2-reasons-to-be-greedy-when-others-are-fearful", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 02:25:35"}, {"id": "4743713", "title": "D.R. Horton: An Industry Leader Worth Considering", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264362572/image_1264362572.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"D.R. Horton New Home Construction During Coronavirus\" data-id=\"1264362572\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3828px\" height=\"2784px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264362572/image_1264362572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264362572/image_1264362572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264362572/image_1264362572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264362572/image_1264362572.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264362572/image_1264362572.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264362572/image_1264362572.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seeki